"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Pravastatin reduces hospitalization for cardiovascular causes",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 431px; height: 282px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The Kaplan-Meier plots of time to first hospitalization show that therapy with pravastatin signifiantly reduces the number of hospitalizations for cardiovascular diagnoses compared to placebo (p = 0.0007).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Data from West of Scotland Coronary Prevention Study Group, J Am Coll Cardiol 1999; 33:909.",
